<para><verbatim>STUN Server - NAT Traversal Server

Implements RFC 5389 STUN protocol for NAT detection and public IP discovery.
</verbatim></para>
<para><verbatim>Relay Server - TURN Relay Service

Provides relay service for P2P connections when direct connection fails.
</verbatim></para>
<para><verbatim>Signaling Server - Connection Coordination Service

Handles device registration, discovery, and connection coordination.
</verbatim></para>
<para><verbatim>DID Service - Device Identity Service

Handles device identity generation, verification, and access token management.
</verbatim> </para>
